Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙 燙燙燙燙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大家來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副得意相讓我們吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 對…對不起 我覺得有點冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣 讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波個頭最大 給最大的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說波波個頭最大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 很好吃哦 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我[最]怎麼樣的呢 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集的話 給葡萄乾最多的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你直接告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙 紙  還有筆 給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個表達面麻的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不能寫 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明日記上就能寫… 給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是沒有墨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次 再讓我試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子 好痛苦 鶴見子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺現在好困
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 一股脫力感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻並沒有生我們的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是原諒我們了還不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果生氣的話 不會做蒸面包的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能正是因為無法原諒 為了責備我們才出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話…話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能寫字的話 一開始就寫出來不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能交談 馬上就能相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳和面麻都太遲鈍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是相信面麻的存在 其實是想獨占面麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好打工攢錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對把煙花做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 一定要讓面麻成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧騰成那樣 一定累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起做煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你能成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還醒著麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 亂跑的話會很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在跑 我也要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳… 無法原諒喜歡仁碳的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周能和我換班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換班？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周四橋梁那邊有施工 日薪很高 准備去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算厭倦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 我說 對面有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子的母親和山先生聯絡過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 伯母她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼並不是叔叔您反對做煙花嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還活在過去裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子出了事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起時間就停滯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望讓她回到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 請不要再讓她回憶起過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說有點大言不慚但是我能理解伯母的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對您女兒… 我喜歡芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為芽衣子做些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也是生活在過去中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做這麼遜的事情讓我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有變呢 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了面麻什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信的話就可以嗎 讓面麻成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼執著于面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過宿海的話就能對話了吧 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過宿海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天會晚點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前送面麻回家先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼不想呆在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論到哪裡都跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 想和大家一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說想和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭發還那麼長嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是和我們一樣成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成長？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會喜歡這個醜女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該算是吧 可愛系？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳你個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本來就算是而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就像是看獨角戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 其實不是這樣吧 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集崩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九話 大家和面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 教你們做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花 煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能讓你們碰火藥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是簡單的打下手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嚇人啊  你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 這是要從竹筒裡出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得紅色多一點比較可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？真是和你的形象不符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 在這裡點火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較容易搬到發射台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}好厲害 好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面麻 好危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放開啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在她跳到你的背上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 面麻 饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 波波 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見面麻卻又能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是過去還是現在都贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我去把橙汁買來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你跑開了 我也得以逃開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻就在旁邊 這讓我很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻看不到面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連說話都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再次見到面麻 但為何只有宿海能見到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為是宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海也是心裡只有面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那時沒有一點改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承認失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都喊他仁碳了 卻又立即改口叫宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛呀 擺出一副把一切都看透的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看透的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫同類人的共鳴麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你這種品質惡劣的人同類 絕對不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說過的那些 我是相當認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說咱倆試著交往下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是對男人沒耐性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮一踢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 什麼漂亮一踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼笑 我是真的大吃一驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于那麼吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我開始熱血了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳 沒有小鳴的布偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴回家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 突然就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是只變化無常的小貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 面麻真的在仁碳身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給面麻實現願望後 面麻不就消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼啦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 到打工時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就要走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 面麻你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和波波一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說想留在這裡 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就留在這裡吧 盡情的留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鬧得太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很高興吧 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}哎 你看那個了？哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季校服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}高中生用雙節棍戰鬥的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初還以為是夏天的怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在已經換上冬裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}少女在香港和僵屍戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 寫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厲害 好厲害啊 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只能用家裡的這個本子寫字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多寫一些吧 再多聊一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}要聊什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 你…那個時候 那個…對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 對了 玩接龍遊戲吧 畫畫接龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那是什麼？看起來像金楚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙肩背包 彈珠 馬裡奧…奧…小手手和小手手的掌紋就是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}注釋：日語假名接龍遊戲 小手手和小手手的掌紋就是幸福是指你雙手合十 幸福的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望遠鏡 開啓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即搜索 面麻隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}您所撥打的電話暫時無人接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 接不上 打工開始了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼走得這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻只是在秘密基地而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼 我卻這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 小面麻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我絕對不要面麻她消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對絕對不要叫仁碳死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是才死掉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 奇怪什麼的 你自己才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 好啦 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 鯉魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯉魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小河裡有一只超級大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻啊 想更近的看一下 看啊 就在那呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在樹根那裡 遊來遊去的 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼哦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳是賴皮蟲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一直一直待在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就待 待在這裡吧 我去替你抓鯉魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仁碳 衣服會濕掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 笨蛋仁碳 會感冒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來呀 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:14.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}何ページも費やして　つづられた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:21.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうしてか一行の　空白を埋められない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:30.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}押花のしおり挟んで　君と転がす 使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:37.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}忘れかけのレンガを　積み上げた場所に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:42.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}海を見渡す坂を駆け上って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}こわいくらいに青い空と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:55.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}右手にサイダー　左手はずっと君を探している
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:01:02.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}そうやって今は僕の方へ　問いつめることもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:09.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}まだ二人はすぐそこにいるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:17.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうかまたあえますようになんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:26.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうかしてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:14.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}填寫了好幾頁 我們那連綿的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:21.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}卻為何填補不了那空白的一行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:30.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}夾上乾花瓣做的書籤 與你共騎上那丟棄的自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:37.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}前往已遺忘的卻堆滿回憶的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:42.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}登上遠望海景的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}藍得刺眼的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:55.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}右手拿著汽水 左手一直追尋著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:01:02.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}現在已沒有需要向我詢問的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:09.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}明明兩人近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:17.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}卻祈望終有一日能相見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:26.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}這是為何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}君と夏の終わり
